- commandDisplayRegistry.ts: 52 command display types with label/icon/color/category
- eventStreamReplayer.ts: Parse and replay eventStream1-4.txt SSE files
- toolResultFormatters.ts: Rich formatters for bash/edit/view/create/test/diff results
- streamingStateManager.ts: Immutable streaming block state tracking
- protocolMetrics.ts: Token usage, latency, tool call stats, performance reports

Modified:
- claudeProtocolParser.ts: Fix NaN bug in calculateBlockDuration for invalid dates
- vite.config.ts: Add vitest test configuration
- package.json: Add vitest + test scripts

